and that the Christmas decorations really only&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:11.040 --> 00:04:18.480
took up about ten percent of her storage locker.
American shoppers love convenience too – not only&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:18.480 --> 00:04:23.520
are there drive through liquor stores in the&nbsp;
United States – there are drive through bars&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:23.520 --> 00:04:30.720
