According to Juliet Schor, a sociologist at&nbsp;
Boston College, the key driver of consumer&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:53.840 --> 00:14:00.000
spending in America is the role that consumption&nbsp;
plays in establishing an individual’s position&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:00.000 --> 00:14:07.200
