consume to keep up with their social group.
&nbsp;

00:14:07.200 --> 00:14:12.160
According to her research, people who have&nbsp;
reference groups that are wealthier than they are&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:12.160 --> 00:14:18.320
- tend to spend more to keep up, and people who&nbsp;
have more modest reference groups, even as they&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:18.320 --> 00:14:24.960
gain in income and wealth, tend to save more.
