spending on services – like restaurants, hotels&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:59.120 --> 00:16:05.920
and haircuts as they prepare for an economic&nbsp;
slowdown. New York magazine reports that Chinese&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:16:05.920 --> 00:16:12.720
websites like Shein and Temu are raising prices&nbsp;
