to see how many buyers would pay more for an&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:16:53.360 --> 00:17:00.080
American manufactured shower head. He gave&nbsp;
shoppers the option to buy a $129 dollar made&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:17:00.080 --> 00:17:07.680
in Asia showerhead or the same product – but&nbsp;
made in America for $239 dollars – the price&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:17:07.680 --> 00:17:16.560
it would cost. He sold 584 of the made in Asia&nbsp;
showerheads and no Made in America showerheads. 
&nbsp;

00:17:16.560 --> 00:17:23.120
Apparently American Apparel ran a similar&nbsp;
experiment in 2017 with a much more modest&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:17:23.120 --> 00:17:30.080
price difference and the majority of customers&nbsp;
still chose the cheaper – imported version.
&nbsp;

